====

INT. STREET - NIGHT

Rain. Endless rain. A single yellow umbrella moves through the crowd.

LOU, 30s, holds the umbrella.

LOU
(to no one)
Always rain.

INT. CAFE - CONTINUOUS

Lou steps inside, closes the umbrella, and shakes it once.

The barista looks up but says nothing.

FADE OUT.

THE END.
